# How to enter your keys

Use this format. **One line per key. No spaces around the `=`.**

---

## Format (copy this block and replace the placeholders)

Save this as a file named **`.env`** in your KLIPORA folder (`E:\KLIPORA`).  
Replace the parts in CAPS with your real values. Do not add spaces before or after `=`.

```
MISSION_CONTROL_URL=https://domainbuddy7-web-klipora-production.up.railway.app
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=8187477791:AAHnYiq_zz5JCEnQeruW5Xt92ehl8xr2lbQ
TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=8232710919
OWNER_TELEGRAM_ID=8232710919
N8N_URL=https://n8n-production-2762.up.railway.app
N8N_API_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIyZjIyNTRhNC1hODhhLTQ2MTMtYjRmNC0xNjFjNjdjOTNkZDciLCJpc3MiOiJuOG4iLCJhdWQiOiJwdWJsaWMtYXBpIiwianRpIjoiNDQ0MTczMDMtODk1OS00NjVjLWI3MmMtM2I0NmQ2NWU1ODI0IiwiaWF0IjoxNzcyOTc2MTEzfQ.s3yKazKQQmDDIyuZmEn09cSRNC8Xw-HinH22Z59KQp4
```

---

## Where to get each value

| Key | Where to get it | Example (fake) |
|-----|-----------------|----------------|
| **MISSION_CONTROL_URL** | Already set above; only change if your API URL is different | `https://domainbuddy7-web-klipora-production.up.railway.app` |
| **TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN** | Telegram: open [@BotFather](https://t.me/BotFather), send `/newbot` or open your bot, copy "API Token" | `123456789:ABCdefGHI...` |
| **TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID** | Telegram: open [@userinfobot](https://t.me/userinfobot), send any message, copy "Id" | `987654321` |
| **OWNER_TELEGRAM_ID** | Same as TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID (your personal Id from @userinfobot) | `987654321` |
| **N8N_URL** | Your n8n address in the browser (no slash at the end) | `https://n8n-production-2762.up.railway.app` |
| **N8N_API_KEY** | n8n → Settings (gear) → API → Create key or copy existing key | `n8n_api_xxxx...` or a long JWT |

---

## Rules

- **No spaces** around the `=` sign.  
  ✅ `TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=abc123`  
  ❌ `TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN = abc123`
- **No quotes** unless the value has spaces (usually it doesn’t).  
  ✅ `TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=123456789`  
  ❌ `TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID="123456789"`
- **One key per line.** Don’t put two keys on the same line.
- **Don’t share this file or paste it in chat.** Keep it only on your computer.

---

## Example (filled in, fake values)

```
MISSION_CONTROL_URL=https://domainbuddy7-web-klipora-production.up.railway.app
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=8187477791:AAHxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=123456789
OWNER_TELEGRAM_ID=8232710919
N8N_URL=https://n8n-production-2762.up.railway.app
N8N_API_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.xxxx
```

Save that as **`.env`** in `E:\KLIPORA` and you’re done. The Telegram bot and the upload script will use it.
